      "text": [
        "١٥٣. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): لَا يَعْدَمُ الصَّبُورُ الظَّفَرَ وَإِنْ طَالَ بِهِ الزَّمَانُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "153. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: The endurer does not miss success although it may take a long time."
